Interface ICharacterReferrer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IFillStyle
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CSMTextSettingsTag, DefineButtonCxformTag, DefineButtonSoundTag, DefineEditTextTag, DefineFontAlignZonesTag, DefineFontInfo2Tag, DefineFontInfoTag, DefineFontNameTag, DefineMorphShape2Tag, DefineMorphShapeTag, DefineScalingGridTag, DefineShape2Tag, DefineShape3Tag, DefineShape4Tag, DefineShapeTag, DefineSpriteTag, DefineText2Tag, DefineTextTag, ExportAssetsTag, FillStyle, FillStyleArray, MorphFillStyle, PlaceObject2Tag, PlaceObject3Tag, PlaceObjectTag, RemoveObjectTag, Shape, ShapeWithStyle, StartSoundTag, StyleChangeRecord, Styles, TextRecord, VideoFrameTag

    public interface ICharacterReferrer
    A SWF tag can refer to one or more SWF tag(s) by the character ID. All the tag classes implements this interface has reference to other tags.
